h of direct detection at the next LHC run. If not\ndiscovered, within a decade the upgraded LHCb and Super B factories may reach\nan indirect sensitivity to a Left-Right scale of 8 TeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Mar 2014 16:18:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Apr 2014 10:38:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
